# KEY DEFINITIONS TO REMEMBER

# $Mod = WINDOWS key or Super key or Mod4
# Mod1 = ALT key
# Control = CTRL key
# Shift = SHIFT key
# Escape = ESCAPE key
# Return = ENTER or RETURN key
# Pause = PAUSE key
# Print = PRINT key
# Tab = TAB key

